---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Deland.io">
    <Header />

    <main class="flex-1">
        <Section class="pt-20 pb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">
                About <span class="text-neon-green">Me</span>.
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-xl md:text-2xl opacity-80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-8"
            >
                I'm an engineer and developer who loves to tinker with
                technology. I admit I'm definitely not a designer, but I do
                appreciate clean, effective software.
            </p>
            <p class="opacity-80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-4">
                My professional life is driven by curiosity and a desire to
                build things that work well. I enjoy diving deep into new tech,
                understanding how systems operate, and solving interesting
                problems.
            </p>
            <p class="opacity-80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
                When I'm not at the keyboard, I'm usually wearing a different
                hat: Dad, Scout Leader, or avid innovative media consumer. I
                love a good TV show or movieâ€”especially if it involves a complex
                heist.
            </p>
        </Section>
    </main>
</Layout>

